This kind of argument is supported by the xparse package:

\documentclass{minimal}
\usepackage{xparse}
\NewDocumentCommand\mycommand{g}{\IfValueTF{#1}{#1}{\vspace{1cm}}}
\begin{document}
test\par
\mycommand
